 - Layout + config of the card must be more like a real letter: clean vertical flow (top signifier/date/salutation, body, closing), far less redundancy (no duplicate hbdMessage as both title and body text, no repeated meta).
 - Remove random corner/trading-card text (id, rarity, "Ultra Rare Holo", "HC-001" etc.) and replace with meaningful, personal, letter-appropriate text (e.g. a date, "For Janell", year as correspondence date, "with love from the universe", or elegant minimal signifier).
