# Notes for the executing agent
- Start by authoring this job (done).
- Immediately follow with full review as the authorizing document.
- Then programme + log.
- Then implement in small, verifiable search_replace steps on the component.
- Pay special attention to the open branch layout and the two places that currently show the random meta (closed top line + open header meta div).
- For the button: make it noticeably larger (increase size classes), move it to a more letter-integrated spot if bottom-right feels redundant (e.g. aligned with sign-off on the right, or as a vertical "unfold" element).
- Slow everything that animates on state change.
- Test mentally on both portrait open and landscape.
- Update any comments to reflect the new "more letter, less card" direction.
- After all changes + gates, update VFS artefacts and close with a nice history entry.